Directions:

Keep refrigerated. Just heat and eat using one of these heating methods. Grilling: Place links on grill about 7-9 inches indirectly above heat source (use Low heat to avoid splitting casings). Cook 7-10 minutes, turning links often. Pan-Heating: Place links in pan, add 1/2 inch water and cover. Simmer on Low heat 10 minutes, turning links often. Microwave: Remove links from pack, place in microwave-safe dish. Add water to cover links. Cover dish, heat on High 1 minute 45 seconds. Turn links, heat again 1 minute 45 seconds.
